<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:1.0cm;line-height:150%;'><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>Sehubungan dengan telah dilakukannya proses kredensialing dari Mitra Bestari Komite&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>Umum</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;RSKIA Kota Bandung,</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>maka dengan ini kami merekomendasikan <strong>a.n.&nbsp;</strong></span><strong><span style='line-height:150%;font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;color:black;'>JUWITA, S.ST&nbsp;</span></strong><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;dengan kemampuan klinik <strong>dapat diterima/tidak di terima*&nbsp;</strong>sebagai&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>PE</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>REKAM MEDIS&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>dan INFORMASI KESEHATAN</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>dan diberikan Kewenangan Kompetensi Profesi (terlampir).</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:1.0cm;line-height:150%;'><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:16px;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;text-align:justify;text-indent:1.0cm;line-height:150%;'><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>Untuk itu diusulkan kepada Direktur Rumah Sakit agar dapat memproses <strong>diterima/tidak diterima*&nbsp;</strong>sebagai&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>PEREKAM MEDIS dan INFORMASI KESEHATAN</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Bookman Old Style",serif;'>serta penugasan klinik ybs.</span></p>
